### Quote Negotiation API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### 1. Health Check - Test if the API is running
GET http://localhost:8080/api/quotes/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Generate Quote - Create a new quote
POST http://localhost:8080/api/quotes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "productName": "Premium Widget",
  "quantity": 100,
  "notes": "Looking for bulk discount on premium widgets for Q1 order"
}

###

### 3. Generate Quote - Another example with different data
POST http://localhost:8080/api/quotes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Jane Smith",
  "productName": "Standard Component",
  "quantity": 50,
  "notes": "Urgent delivery required, willing to pay premium for fast shipping"
}

###

### 4. Get Quote by ID - Retrieve a specific quote (replace {id} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/quotes/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Get Quote by ID - Another example
GET http://localhost:8080/api/quotes/2
Accept: application/json

###

### Environment Variables (Optional)
### You can define variables for different environments
### @baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
### @apiPath = /api/quotes

### Example using variables:
# GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/health
